4 System Monitoring Script

Example: Monitor CPU and Memory usage

First install:

pip install psutil

Python script:

import psutil

cpu = psutil.cpu_percent(interval=1)
memory = psutil.virtual_memory().percent

print("CPU Usage:", cpu, "%")
print("Memory Usage:", memory, "%")

Use cases:

Server monitoring

Alert systems

DevOps dashboards

