6. Automating Log Cleanup

Example: Delete old log files

import os
import time

path = "/var/log/myapp"

for file in os.listdir(path):
    file_path = os.path.join(path, file)

    if os.stat(file_path).st_mtime < time.time() - 7 * 86400:
        os.remove(file_path)
        print("Deleted:", file)

Deletes logs older than 7 days.

